params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The name of the entry group that contains the entries to list. Can be provided in URL format.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: The maximum number of items to return. Default is 10. Maximum limit is 1000. Throws an invalid argument if page_size is more than 1000.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Pagination token that specifies the next page to return. If empty, the first page is returned.

params.name: data.read_mask
params.description: The fields to return for each entry. If empty or omitted, all fields are returned. For example, to return a list of entries with only the name field, set read_mask to only one path with the name value.
